videos.description: Teaira McCowan muscles for the rebound and rises for the layup and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Mississippi State's McCowan grabs offensive board for putback

videos.description: Jordan Frericks blocks a shot on the defensive end and Sophie Cunningham beats everyone down the court for a transition layup.
videos.headline: Frericks' hustle leads to fast-break bucket for Missouri

videos.description: Sophie Cunningham misses a 3-pointer, but Amber Smith feeds her the ball again and she drills it on her second attempt.
videos.headline: Missouri's Cunningham makes good on second look

videos.description: Lauren Aldridge drains two consecutive 3-pointers to give Missouri a 10-point lead.
videos.headline: Aldridge knocks down back-to-back treys for Missouri

videos.description: Victoria Vivians knocks down the a midrange jumper to give Mississippi State the lead for the first time since the first quarter.
videos.headline: Vivians gives Mississippi State the lead

videos.description: A tipped ball falls into Jordan Frericks' hands for a wide-open layup.
videos.headline: Frericks at right place, right time for Missouri bucket

videos.description: Sophie Cunningham buries the game-tying 3-pointer with nine seconds remaining.
videos.headline: Cunningham ties game for Missouri

videos.description: Victoria Vivians gets into the paint and hits a jump shot to give Mississippi State the lead.
videos.headline: Vivians buries game-winning jumper for Mississippi State

videos.description: In a game that went back and forth in the fourth quarter, the No. 2 Bulldogs take the lead late and hold on to defeat the No. 15 Tigers 57-53.
videos.headline: Mississippi State edges Missouri in thriller
